        <mxCell id="C33gGLDRph4QMVR-yTKw-72" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;The workflow uses isolated parallel execution for each test suite. This ensures that the failuire of one test job does not fail-early the other remaining concurrent jobs to ensure that the test coverage artifacts for each suite are uploaded.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;However, the next quality gate (the &lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;build&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;job) will require all previous jobs to have succeeded before the deployment cycle will proceed further.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
